# Raw data directory

This directory contains unprocessed HTML files and raw scraped data.

## Structure
- `html/` - Raw HTML files from web scraping
- `json/` - Raw JSON responses from APIs
- `images/` - Downloaded images and media files

## Usage
Files in this directory are automatically generated by the scraper.
Do not manually edit files in this directory as they may be overwritten.

## Cleanup
Files older than 30 days are automatically cleaned up by the scraper.
